    </tr> -->
    <tr>
      <td><h4 class="heading-small">Step 3</h4><p>Week 3</p></td>
      <td><h4 class="heading-small">Complete the e-tray exercise and the video interview</h4><p>We'll send you a link to an e-tray exercise to complete and ask you to do a video interview.</p>
      </td>
